Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? How did a pachislot magazine reporter \Nend up investigating boxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Different things have intertwined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot of ridicule \Nabout that title match of Mr. Kasamatsu, born 1973.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:19.03,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu - the Invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, Mr. Kasamatsu was popular for his intention of becoming world-famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu - King of the Rookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, I was still fighting in the 4-round league. \NI remember those days clear as a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, it happened \N4 days before his title match, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since his debut, Kasamatsu Ryu \Nkept winning with a thrust of a steamroller,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually becoming East Japan's rookie star, \Nentering the rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was determined to maintain that momentum \Nto conquer the Japan's title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, during a routine roadwork, \Nhe got a ligament rupture in the car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu's tragic accident \NTitle Match - Hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.26,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu - Unrecoverable!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,His boxing career seemed by all means over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.23,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu's retirement for rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:28.13,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Ryu's comeback \NFrom despair, he is reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From the state which seemed hopeless to any, \Nhe ascended again, in spite of all ridicules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu seemed more fearless than ever \Nafter those two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,making this time the most productive in his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the main factor \Nin Mr. Kasamatsu's miraculous comeback is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is Akira.\NThe prime reason for me to keep winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, your next title match...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm winning it. Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For my son Akira, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... The best in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You move well, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see all of his punches. \NAnd my reflexes are perfect, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You came a long way. Don't you think \Nit's about time you finally become a champion? Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it... \NWhat is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, start moving! \NUse your goddamn legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He is coming! \NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is going on? \NMy leg... won't move an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Old wound strikes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You wake up screaming almost every night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow I'll put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win. \NTo quit this circle of self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For you. And also \Nfor that little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some fresh air while running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bell... Bell... Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Replay... Replay... Replay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Which punch will this guy try next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! It's only round two! \NMove it! Move, goddamnit! {TODO: I feel something's off here in the futatsu part, not exactly the round two sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must... I must... defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya? \NYou eat here today as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the rest of the food here is good as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have special fried oysters with a big rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. \NOne of special oysters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira is hanging out here every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in our custody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,While that riffraff is having his fun in pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kasamatsu was once a mighty fellow, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it took him one title match lost \Nto run out of steam completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He neglected the trainings completely - \Npachislot, pachislot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife also grew cold on him \Nand left the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So Akira is forced \Nto spend his lonely days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu used to constantly claim to do it all for Akira, \Nbut the truth is -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,has he really done something good for Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But he did not retire yet, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He is still boxing to this day, \Ntrying his best, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.\NEven if he does, it's no better than quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for once, have not seen Ryu \Ntraining a single time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, he was really gifted. \NI'd never act this was in his shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy like him is not supposed \Nto end his path in this miserable way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, for how many years, exactly, \Nhave you been a boxer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. And how old were you \Nwhen you started?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we not discussed this \Nenough times, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I have been advised to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go on barking in vain like that, \NI'll have no future aside from being an underdog anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Really thinking of it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I lost that title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have never been subjected to unfair matchmaking. \NAnd you have never been seen as an underdog's either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this - \Nmerely a product of your low spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is, \NI understand your feelings perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, \Npoint out what's wrong with me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't tell me more than that, \NI'll have my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All in all, how many comebacks have you already had? {Again, I don't see the connection and why he said it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your father is a boxer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This father of yours... you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your current father, \Nor your old days' father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They are both the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad will be dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, do you know where does the wind come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,From everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's the depths of my heart \Nwhere it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Akira, \Nwhy don't I give you a piggyback ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \NGinya, stop, you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Quit fidgeting! \N- Embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... \NNo, that took too heavy a toll on my tallness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got what you had coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Only thanks to someone's dumb fidgeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All in all, how many comebacks have you already had?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to lie to me? {Might as well be anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro boxer, Mr. Kasamatsu Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more, \NI want to challenge you to a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening. In contrary to you, \NI play pachislot for fun, not for fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a child \Nto be playing it for fun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving things half-complete \Nis only excusable for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as using pachislot \Nto escape the responsibility for giving up boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to prove me wrong,\Naccept my challenge, Kasamatsu Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lose, you quit pachislot forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hear your answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kasamatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I agreed to bother to come, \Nbut I can't help wondering where to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as Akira saw this place, \Nhe figured it'd be the best possible ring for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:13.20,Song,,0,0,0,,Ryu = Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one to score three Bigs, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever loses, never plays pachislot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let us get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That speed and nimbleness of eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing such a slotter outside Slothium \Nis not something you do on a day by day basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that also means \NI have no excuse to lose to him, whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NWhere did all that recent cockiness go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I said. \NWe're not playing games here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One more left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever hits Big first, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one to stop a reel, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. \NI've had enough of his trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. It's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win and shut that brat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in the world does goddess of victory \Nhate my whole existence this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't forget what you promised us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, do not lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely cannot see dad \Nlosing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is already apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Mr. Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to forgive me, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For some time, you'll have to do without treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope you're okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For you and me, \Nsome dark times may be coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely fine! \NI won't complain! Not once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want just one thing... \NFor you to give me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once more. Once more, I want you \Nto step into the ring and piggyback me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to give me a piggyback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I heard you. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
