Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My bewilderment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NDays Gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
